  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0bc7\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b9a \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Let us speedily establish political stability under the leadership of a new President - Vijetasa Assimilation",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Justice Wijetasa Rajapaksh has told the Sri Lankan Ambassador to Thailand that we will quickly establish political stability and submit the 22nd amendment of the Constitution to the Parliament for approval.",
        "Thai Ambassador to Sri Lanka Bhoj Hanbol met and discussed with the Minister of Justice, Prisons and Constitutional Reform Wijetasa Rajapaksa today at the Ministry of Justice.",
        "During this, attention was paid to further increase the long standing economic, political and cultural cooperation between the two countries.",
        "Under the leadership of the new president, steps will be taken to bring political stability and normalization of the economy to Sri Lanka.",
        "Also, the minister told the ambassador that we are taking steps to submit the 22nd amendment of the constitution to the parliament and approve it.",
        "Also, the minister recalled that in 2016, he had the opportunity to deliver the keynote speech at the United Nations International Vesak Festival held in Thailand and in 2017, when the festival was held in Sri Lanka, Thailand provided massive cooperation for it.",
        "The Minister also reminded the cooperation that Thailand is receiving for the reconstruction of Buddhism and for economic and religious cultural development in Sri Lanka by taking steps to restore the Buddhist upasampada to this country.",
        "We hope that the current problematic situation in Sri Lanka will be over and economic stability will be achieved.",
        "According to a statement issued by the Ministry of Justice, the Ambassador to Thailand said that we are ready to provide diplomatic assistance."
      ],
